            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Plutonium samples 2 in. in diameter were cut from",
                "large 0.016 in. aluminum sheets that had been",
                "uniformly coated with several layers of lacquer",
                " (cellulose nitrate dissolved in amyl acetate)",
                "containing plutonium nitrate dissolved in acetone.",
